comments: Gobert (MIN) establishes himself in Turner's (IND) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Nesmith (IND) brings his hand forward towards Edwards' (MIN) front and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Nesmith (IND) initiates contact with Edwards's (MIN) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Turner (IND) establishes himself in McDaniels' (MIN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Hield (IND) is already in Gobert's (MIN) path and absorbs the contact.
McDaniels (MIN) extends his hands into Haliburton's (IND) upper body, driving him off of his legally obtained rebounding position.
Gobert (MIN) and Hield (IND) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Nesmith (IND) cleanly deflects the ball away from Russell (MIN) as they pursue the loose ball.
Hield (IND) places his hand momentarily on Gobert's (MIN) side and he immediately removes his hand as marginal contact occurs.
Russell (MIN) is bracing for the contact from Hield (IND) and marginal contact occurs as he releases away from the contact.
Turner (IND) and Gobert (MIN) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
McDaniels (MIN) places his hand to Haliburton's (IND) side and marginal body contact occurs at the end of his drive.
Hield (IND) is moving alongside Nowell's (MIN) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together at the end of the drive.
Gobert (MIN) establishes himself in Nembhard's (IND) path and is firming up over his left leg when contact occurs.
Nembhard (IND) places his hand momentarily on Gobert's (MIN) side and immediately removes his hand as marginal contact occurs.
After initially making contact with the ball, Hield (IND) slides his hand off of the ball and makes contact with Gobert's (MIN) arm as he defends the shot near the rim.
Turner (IND) establishes himself in McDaniels's (MIN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Turner (IND) establishes himself in Rivers' (MIN) path and absorbs the contact.
Gobert (MIN) is moving alongside Hield's (IND) path and marginal contact occurs as Gobert cleanly blocks the shot attempt.
Gobert (MIN) cleanly blocks the shot attempt before it touches the backboard.
Nesmith (IND) and McDaniels (MIN) come together off ball and marginal contact occurs as they turn to move down the court in transition.
Nesmith (IND) commits a take foul on Edwards (MIN). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Turner (IND) legally contests Gobert's (MIN) layup attempt.
Nembhard (IND) loses control of ball at the end of his drive and marginal contact occurs as Rivers' (IND) brushes his hand as he regains the possession.
